CustomField.description: Used to flag Service Territories assigned to Subcontractors of MSN. This is e.g. used in the Flow "Assign to Subcontractor" in order to give the user a list of all subcontractor territories the service appointment can be assigned to.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Please tick this, if this Service Territory is used for a Subcontractor.
CustomField.label: Subcontractor Service Territory
